products.title: Oculus Modern Grey Magic Screen Roller Blind
products.metadescription: The oculus modern grey magic screen roller blind is mid-grey in tone and will harmonise with many colour schemes. Although we love the colour the real story here is the magic screen fabric. The unique fabric design ensures daytime privacy but allows a view to the outside too.
